   <text>
      <body>
         <div type="translation">
            <ab>[- - -] I will measure out and pay everything without any deception or subterfuge. And if I do not do as aforesaid, I will pay the damages and costs and a fine of five hundred drachmai of silver and to the public treasury the same, and this note shall be nonetheless valid wherever produced; and the cession of the three arourai which you made to me, Heron, alone, shall remain valid and legal for me. Year 1 of Tiberius Claudius Caesar Augustus Germanicus Imperator, Kaisareios 1.</ab>
